”，应进尽进、应贷尽贷，满足项目合理融资需求。 相关政策发布以来，政策效果已经开始显现，房地产开发投资、新建商品房销售等主要指标降幅继续收窄，特别是9月底以来，一手房看房量、到访量、签约量明显增加，二手房交易量持续上升，市场出现了积极的变化。媒体报道，多地房地产政策支持力度加码，一线城市楼市全线回温。下一步，住建部将会同有关部门，坚决贯彻党中央、国务院决策部署，一项一项抓落实，把政策效应充分释放出来，更多惠及人民群众。住建部：年底前，“白名单”增资到4万亿 | 每经网"},"attached_info":"CkEImYr1hpXb5/s+EAMaCTExMTIwNDAzMiCQ78G4BjAAONoBQA5yCjExMzY3MzEwODd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"11 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-526f537f45bfe763c9d0baa48bab630e_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1729182150.518324","card_id":"Q_863155090","target":{"id":863155090,"title":"「为什么选择我们公司」？当秋招生面试被问到这句话时，完美回答是什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/863155090","type":"question","created":1728839985,"answer_count":45,"follower_count":95,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[622,3683687,3695471,3721970],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8ImYr1hpXb5/s+EAMaCTExMTEzMTQyNiCxgrC4BjAAOF9AD3IJODYzMTU1MDkweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"11 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-ebec8f64d023e6f0042b9ecab3161da1_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"16_1729182150.518477","card_id":"Q_292193783","target":{"id":292193783,"title":"怎么看待《从姑获鸟开始》作者活儿该？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/292193783","type":"question","created":1535359446,"answer_count":56,"follower_count":191,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1873,153619],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"活儿该宝藏作者"},"attached_info":"Cj8ImYr1hpXb5/s+EAMaCDI3MjA4ODc4INbzjtwFMAA4vwFAEHIJMjkyMTkzNzgzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTS